Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.51,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs35\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\3c&H000000&\an7\pos(20,80)}虽然可能也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.51,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs35\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\3c&H000000&\an7\pos(20,115)}真的假的？！God Cauldron\N竟然输给了废物龙王？
